column3: A rookie on the rise with razor-sharp claws─the ferocious feline Black Cat!
The match is decided! Victory goes to the challenger!
The starlet with a sting─the adorable-but-deadly, sweet-but-poisonous Honey B. Lovely!
Tonight he explodes in the ring once more... The man you love to hate with a fiery passion─the Brute Bomber!
Wielding both magic and machina, she's a witch for a new age. The wondrous Wicked Thunder!
Damn it... No choice but to withdraw.
In a shocking turn of events, Wicked Thunder has fled the ring! Our unstoppable upstart is victorious!
